high_descs: Go right and then right again to face the cabinet above the small black table.
Open the upper cabinet on the left and take the salt shaker on the right out of the cabinet.
Move back and face the small black table to the left of the counter.
Put the salt shaker down on the black table.
Face the cabinet above the black table.
Take the salt shaker out of the cabinet above the black table.
Back up to face the black table again.
Put the salt shaker on the black table.
anns.task_desc: Put two salt shakers on a table.

high_descs: Turn around an go to the cabinet above small black table near the left corner.
Take the salt shaker on the right out of the cabinet.
Move back from the cabinet.
Place the salt shaker on the right corner of the small black table.
Go back to the cabinet above.
Remove the remaining salt shaker from the cabinet.
Move back from the cabinet.
Place the salt shaker between the first salt shaker and another in the middle.
anns.task_desc: Move the salt shakers from the cabinet to the table.

high_descs: Turn right, walk to the long white table, turn right and walk to the small black table.
Take out the right salt shaker from the cabinet above the small black table.
Take a step backwards from where you are at.
Place the salt shaker to the right of the tomato on the small black table.
Look up to the shelf above from where you are at.
Take the other salt shaker out from the cabinet.
Take a step backwards from where you are at.
Place the salt shaker to next to the other salt shaker on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Transfer the two salt shakers from the cabinet above the small black table onto the table.
